      "title": "RANIL WICKREMESINGHE WINS PRESIDENTIAL VOTE",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Acting President Ranil Wickremesinghe has won the Presidential election held in Parliament a short while ago, the Speaker announced.",
        "Ranil Wickremesinghe\u00a0obtained 134 votes while Dullas Alahapperume obtained 82 votes and Anura Kumara Dissanayake has obtained 3 votes."
